## Example environment variables (DO NOT put real secrets here)

## Domain allowlist (server-side)
# Regex used to validate email domains
ALLOWED_DOMAINS_REGEXP="@example\.org"

## App URL
PUBLIC_LOGIN_URL="http://localhost:5173"

## Appwrite configuration
APPWRITE_ENDPOINT="https://cloud.example.com/v1"
APPWRITE_PROJECT="<appwrite_project_id>"
APPWRITE_KEY="<appwrite_api_key>"
APPWRITE_DATABASE_ID="<appwrite_database_id>"
APPWRITE_CONSENT_EVENTS_COLLECTION_ID="<appwrite_collection_id>"
APPWRITE_CURRENT_CONSENTS_COLLECTION_ID="<appwrite_collection_id>"

## OpenAlex API key (required for authenticated API access)
OPENALEX_API_TOKEN="<openalex_api_key>"
